                                <div class="page_text">
                                    The Government of Kerala has introduced various scholarships awarded to meritorious
                                    students of outstanding performance in the education sector as well as to the
                                    students of socially and economically backward categories. The Higher Education
                                    Department of Government of Kerala is entrusted with the responsibility of selection
                                    and disbursement of various scholarships to Under Graduate and Post Graduate
                                    Streams. The college has a very active Scholarship Cell to give the students timely
                                    information and guidance on various scholarships and freeships they are entitled
                                    to., Mr. Mohamed Sadiqu P.A. Assistant Professor, Department of Arabic is the Nodal
                                    Officer of Scholarships at the college. Our students have received many scholarships
                                    being offered by various government and non-governmental agencies.Our College
                                    sponsored Shihab Thangal Memorial Fellowship, State Merit Scholarship, Suvarna
                                    Jubilee Merit Scholarship, Blind/PH Scholarship, Higher Education Scholarship,
                                    Central Sector Scholarship, Snehapoorvam Scholarship, Postmatric Scholarship, Muslim
                                    Girls Scholarship, CH Muhammed Koya Scholarship, Indian Jeeva Karunya Trust
                                    scholarship are a few to mention.
